==English==

===Adjective===
'''westerly'''

# Situated in the [[west]]
# (''of wind'') coming from the west

===Adverb===
'''westerly'''

# Towards the west
# Used by Land Surveyors when they do not want to be specific (not Astronomic West)

===Noun===
'''westerly''' (''plural'' westerlies)

# A westerly wind or [[storm]]

